snippet.title: Spider-Man 4 Unreleased Movie Tie-in Game (XBOX 360)
snippet.description:
More Info: https://www.obscuregamers.com/builddb/spider-man_4/

Unlike the Wii version that leaked before this is based on a different engine, most assets/menus being recycled from the 2009 Prototype game.
